    'body' => 'Eris Reddoch writes:

>On 06/30/98 at 04:52 AM,  Hans Rancke-Madsen <rancke@diku.dk> said:
> 
>>>Look in your Traveller book regarding TL of a planet.
>>>The maximum TL that can be LOCALLY PRODUCED.
