    'body' => 'Bruce Allan Macintosh wrote:
>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
>And even with it\'s agility-5, I think the _Gionetti_ would have problems
>with an AHL
The first ship to get a hit with its meson spinal wins. 3G acceleration
